### Survey CRUD API Endpoints
### Base URL: http://localhost:5000

### Get all surveys
GET http://localhost:5000/api/surveys

###

### Get survey by ID
GET http://localhost:5000/api/surveys/3fa85f64-5717-4562-b3fc-2c963f66afa6

###

### Get survey by name
GET http://localhost:5000/api/surveys/name/Demo 2015

###

### Search surveys by name (partial match)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/surveys/search?term=Demo

###

### Get surveys by status (0=Initial, 1=InProgress, 2=Complete)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/surveys/status/0

###

### Create new survey
POST http://localhost:5000/api/surveys
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "surveyName": "My New Survey",
  "status": 0,
  "lockStatus": 0,
  "unlockKeyType": 0,
  "errorsExist": false,
  "surveyNotes": "This is a test survey"
}

###

### Update existing survey
PUT http://localhost:5000/api/surveys/3fa85f64-5717-4562-b3fc-2c963f66afa6
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": "3fa85f64-5717-4562-b3fc-2c963f66afa6",
  "surveyName": "Updated Survey Name",
  "status": 1,
  "lockStatus": 0,
  "unlockKeyType": 0,
  "errorsExist": false,
  "surveyNotes": "Updated notes"
}

###

### Delete survey
DELETE http://localhost:5000/api/surveys/3fa85f64-5717-4562-b3fc-2c963f66afa6

###

### Get survey statistics
GET http://localhost:5000/api/surveys/3fa85f64-5717-4562-b3fc-2c963f66afa6/stats

###
